    "takeaway": "PLAN: For future reference, always recall the 'rule of 2-3 cm' for stoma height. Consider the patient's body habitus, previous surgeries, and lifestyle when selecting the stoma site. Emphasize the importance of stoma maturation in preventing complications. Review ostomy appliance selection and management as a complementary skill.",
