      "plan": "Further education should focus on the aggressive nature of biliary cancers, the limitations of surgical intervention, and the importance of early detection and multidisciplinary care.  Case studies illustrating the challenges of resectability and the role of palliative strategies are highly recommended.  A deeper dive into the molecular subtypes of cholangiocarcinoma is also warranted."
