    "takeaway": "PLAN: I would recommend a review of the pathophysiology of vitamin B12 absorption, the impact of gastrectomy on calcium and phosphorus homeostasis, and the clinical presentation and management of metabolic bone disease in post-gastrectomy patients. A detailed discussion of the differences between Billroth I and Billroth II reconstructions regarding nutrient absorption is also warranted. Finally, emphasize the importance of long-term nutritional surveillance and supplementation.",
